close_time.descr: The unix timestamp of the time the vote was closed

end_time.descr: The unix timestamp of the ending time of voting_round

is_bootstrapped.descr: Whether or not the contract has been bootstrapped with answers

metadata_ipfs_cid.descr: The IPFS content ID of the voting_round metadata file

nft_asset_id.descr: The asset ID of a result NFT if one has been created

nft_image_url.descr: The IPFS URL of the default image to use as the media of the result NFT

option_counts.descr: The number of options for each question

quorum.descr: The minimum number of voters to reach quorum

snapshot_public_key.descr: The public key of the Ed25519 compatible private key that was used to encrypt entries in the vote gating snapshot

start_time.descr: The unix timestamp of the starting time of voting_round

vote_id.descr: The identifier of this voting_round round

voter_count.descr: The minimum number of voters who have voted
